## 8. No request logging / correlation IDs
Add `morgan` or `pino-http` plus a request-ID middleware. Without this, incident response and abuse detection are effectively blind.

## 9. No graceful shutdown
On `SIGTERM`/`SIGINT`, call `server.close()` so in-flight requests finish and connections drain — important behind a load balancer.

```js
