The file is small, but it has several gaps worth addressing before it's production-ready. Below are concrete, prioritized suggestions.

## 1. Missing global error handling

There is no error-handling middleware and no handler for uncaught async errors. Express will respond with an HTML stack trace by default, which leaks implementation details.

```js
