if (!Number.isFinite(PORT) || PORT <= 0) throw new Error('Invalid PORT');
```

## 6. Startup vs. Export Coupling

Calling `app.listen()` at import time makes `app.js` hard to test (tests that `require('./app')` open a real socket). Split:

```js
