- **Rate limiting**: mitigates brute-force and scraping; tighten on auth endpoints (e.g., 5/min).
- **Validate every user input** at the boundary. Reject unknown fields; coerce and bound-check numbers; validate string length and character sets. Prefer a schema library (`zod`) over ad-hoc checks.
